name: Cosmos Necklace
description:
A modern creation with enough of a patina to give it some mystery, just like the heavens on which this necklace is based. Sterling silver discs are strung together with small rivets making all the parts move.

Chain and clasp are handmade.

Measures: 20 inches long.

Comes in a beautiful package // Please visit our About page for care instructions when cleaning jewelry that has been intentionally oxidized.

name: Sea Shelf Pendant
description:
The ocean and all that meets the ocean has always held a fascination, particularly rock formations sculpted by the sea. This pendant gets its inspiration from the slabs of dark rock with perfectly parallel groves that reach out into the surf.

Made from sterling silver, encrusted with gold dust and weathered with patina, it almost has the effect of petrified wood.

Measures: Approx. 1 1/2 inches long x 3/4 inch wide

Comes in a beautiful package // Please visit our About page for care instructions when cleaning jewelry that has been intentionally oxidized.

(This item is sold out. We can arrange to make a similar one, however, because it is unique, no two can be exactly alike. Please inquire.)

name: Homage to Klimt Pendant
description:
An elegant and quirky pendant studded with individual cubes in sterling silver and 22K gold, reminiscent of a cobblestone street, mounted onto a sterling silver slab. Cubes are hollow, so while this pendant has real presence, it isn't heavy or weighing down its rubber cord (with magnetic closure).

Measures: 1 1/2 inches tall x 7/8 inches wide x approx. 1/8 inch deep

Comes beautifully wrapped. See our About page for care instructions when cleaning jewelry that is intentionally oxidized to have a patina.

name: Garden Path Ring
description:
Like a tiny path of paving stones, this unique ring has the boldness of statement ring without the weight since it's made of hollow boxes. It's both sophisticated and whimsical. Oxidized sterling silver and 22K gold. Measures: Top of ring: approx. 1 inch in diameter x 1/4 inch deep Made to order. Please allow 3â€“5 days, not including shipping. This ring can be made adjustable. Please inquire. Comes in a beautiful package.

description:
Open these sterling silver earrings to reveal a secret space.

Insert your favorite poem, an empowering mantra, a sexy thought.

Or you can soak a small piece of cotton in your favorite perfume and squirrel it away.

Oxidized sterling silver

name: Message Wonderbox Earrings
description:
These unique open-frame earrings in oxidized sterling silver have a set of 4 lines of text from Anais Nin's book of erotica tucked into the corner, readable from both sides of the earrings.

What's on the other side? You're going to have to find out.

Can be made special order.

description:
These might have been inspired by how much time we spend in the kitchen. Perhaps they'd be the perfect gift for that culinary friend. In oxidized sterling silver, they have a rustic but modern look. Each spoon's delicate rim is sanded to reveal a little silver sparkle. Comes in a beautiful package.

name: Riverbed Pendant
description:
As mysterious and compelling as a winding river, this unique pendant is made with a Japanese alloy called shakudo that combines approximately 95% copper with 5% gold, which is then fused onto sterling silver. We make this alloy in our studio. A patina, plus the process of making the alloy creates this dynamic, yet serene surface effect. There will only ever be one just like this. So you know you will be wearing something completely unique. This is a hollow box, so while it appears solid, it has an appealing lightness to it. Measures: 2 1/4 inches long x 3/4 inch wide x 1/8 inch deep 18" rubber cord with magnetic closure included. Comes in a beautiful package.

Tags: shakudo, gold, silver, copper, rectangle, pendant, swirl, pattern

name: Terra Pendant
description:
A pendant in rich chocolate tones, with hints of gold uses shakudoâ€”a Japanese alloy of mostly copper with a small percentage of gold that we make here in the studio. It is then combined with sterling silver and patinas to give an earthy feel, with a subtle sparkle. While having a strong presence, the pendant is a lightweight hollow box. It comes on a brown suede cord to tie at the length of your choice. Pendant measures: 2 3/8 long x 1 inch wide x approx. 1/8 inch deep Comes in a beautiful package.
